  "title": "PLUMBING SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p>1. Review and monitor site construction activities to ensure work completion as</p>\n<p>schedule.</p>\n<p>2, Manpower arrangement and supervise/manage site arrangement.</p>\n<p>3. Attend meetings, including but not limited to site meetings and inspections</p>\n<p>4, Installation Work, installing pipes, fixtures (toilets, sinks, tubs, etc.), and</p>\n<p>appliances that use water or gas.<br>\n5. Repair, fixing leaks, clogs, and damaged pipes or fixtures.</p>\n<p>6, Maintenance, performing routine checks and maintenance to prevent problems</p>\n<p>and ensure systems are functioning correctly.</p>\n<p>7, System Testing</p>\n<p>8, Code Compliance</p>\n<p>9, Customer Interaction</p>\n<p><strong>Required Skills and Qualifications:</strong></p>\n<p>1, Technical Knowledge</p>\n<p>2, Troubleshooting Skills</p>\n<p>3, Communication Skills</p>\n<p>4, Problem-Solving</p>\n<p>5, Safety Awareness</p>\n<p>6, Knowledge of water supply, waste disposal, and gas systems</p>\n<p>7, Ability to read and interpret blueprints and technical drawings</p>\n<p>8, Good communication (especially for customer interaction)</p>",
